Reports a labeled statement inside a <code>switch</code> statement, which 
often results from a typo.
<p>Example:</p>
<pre><code>
    <b>switch</b>(x)
    {
        <b>case</b> 1:
        case2:   //typo!
        <b>case</b> 3:
            <b>break</b>;
    }
</code></pre>
